      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KEEN ON KEV (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 29.97 beating Jumbuk Sachin. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to measure up again. VERA JAKIT (3) missed the frame last time but prior to that was an effortless T3 RSTW winner (29.99) at this track, scoring by 2.5 lengths. Has the ability and expected to do much better. WINCKIE BALE (4) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (30.18) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Solid record here winning two races. Overdue and expected to feature again. AXEL'S RADAR (6) cannot be underestimated.",
